{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_07_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 大きな翼で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "負けないために……負けないよう差を埋めるために\nどうするのが正解なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To not lose… to close the gap so we won’t lose‚\nWhat’s the right thing to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "難しい問いだな。ただ一つ言えるのは\n勝敗は技術だけで決まるものじゃない、ってことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a tough question. But one thing’s for sure:\nVictory and defeat aren’t decided by skill alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.7651246708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんでしょうか？\n……ああ、でも確かに。そうかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\n…Ah‚ but you’re right. Maybe that’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.8084580422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリの時\n私達は万全に仕上がっていて、勢いだってあった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nWe were fully prepared‚ and we had momentum.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9817902248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、サニーピースに負けた……\n技術だけじゃない……何かが、敗因だったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we lost to Sunny Peace…\nIt wasn’t just skill… something else was the reason for our defeat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9817903202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。だから、それを踏まえて……\n「負けないために」って考えは、いったん捨ててみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. So‚ based on that…\nLet’s try putting aside the thought of “not losing” for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "かわりに、「なぜ負けたくないのか」の理由を\n徹底的に掘り下げてみるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead‚ let’s thoroughly explore\nthe reason why you don’t want to lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3999763855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.8566427868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……捨てちゃうんですか？\nどうして「負けたくないのか」を、掘り下げる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… We’re putting it aside?\nWhy do we have to… explore why we “don’t want to lose?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4028557778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "でもそんなの、「負けたくないから」としか\n他に、負けたくない理由なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s… the only reason I can think of. “Because we don’t want to lose.”\nThere’s no other reason…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、そうして結論を急ぐのがいけないんですね\nもっとちゃんと、考え抜かないと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ rushing to a conclusion is what’s wrong.\nI have to think it through more carefully――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6237.143166899998,
          "startTime": 73.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9603.809833499994,
          "startTime": 76.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6764200212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "――あ、すみません。すみれからメッセージが……\n……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Ah‚ excuse me. I got a message from Sumire…\n…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8333348593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8333348593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは、なんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did Sumire say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2054836116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2732387465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "あの、私、優やすみれとも話し合ってみます\nすみれも、私達に相談があるみたいなので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ I’ll discuss it with Yu and Sumire.\nSumire said she has something to discuss with us too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.200001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "その時に、「負けたくない」理由と向き合ってみます\nトリエルのリーダーとして、しっかりと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I’ll try to face the reason why we “don’t want to lose” then.\nAs TRINITYAiLE’s leader‚ I’ll…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7333348593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2158469441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。この答えは、自分達で見つけることに意味がある\n瑠依達なら見つけられるって、信じてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Finding this answer yourself is what’s important.\nI believe you can find it‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666681927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.5062552376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "はい……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5062552376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7556203289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 113.8889574769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依達は無事、答えを見つけ出したようだ）\n（その上で、新曲でランキング五位に挑みたいという）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It seems like Rui found the answer.）\n（And they want to challenge the fifth-ranked group with a new song.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5666681927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "既存曲でも戦えるとは思います\nでもそれだと、結局、いつもの私達でしかない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe we can fight with our existing songs.\nBut if we do that‚ we’ll just be the usual us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333348593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "誰が見ても明らかなこの下剋上を成し遂げるには\nいつもの私達を超えなくちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To pull off this obvious upset‚\nWe have to surpass the usual us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.900001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "そのための大きな翼が必要なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need big wings to do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7012659473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "けど、これから曲を準備するとなると、レッスンは\nよりハードになるぞ？　勝てる見込みだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if we’re going to prepare a new song from now‚ the lessons\nWill be even harder. And the chances of winning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7884320236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "望むところです\nそれでこその、挑戦じゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what we want.\nThat’s what makes it a challenge‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8556973223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "負けるかもしれなくても、挑戦することに意味がある\nその姿こそ、ファンのみんなが求めているもので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we might lose‚ there’s meaning in challenging ourselves.\nThat’s the kind of thing our fans want to see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.800001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私達のエールを打ち返してくれる声援に\n励まされるから、トリエルはさらに高く飛べる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And those cheers that return our call…\nEncourage us‚ so TRINITYAiLE can fly even higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.289547579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
